data.meta_description: Team, Jiangsu Kemao New Materials Technology Co.,Ltd
data.text:
Mr CHEN Dong

Executive Director

Mr Chen founded Jiangyin Fumao Chemical Fiber Factory in 2003. The business grew from a single line chemical fiber manufacturer to three-line chemical fiber and polymer nylon new material manufacturer. He received Jiangyin outstanding entrepreneur award and is the vice president of Jiangyin Chamber of Commerce. He joint Kemao China in 2016 as the General Manager.

Ms CHEN Fang

Executive Director

Ms Chen studied in Nanjing Sanjiang University and Kobe University in Japan. She joint Kemao China upon graduating from university in 2009. Her work at Kemao China have been well acknowledged by her colleagues and customers of the business, and has assisted the company in gaining reputation in the field over the years. She awarded the “development and innovation talents” award by Wuxi city.

Mr WANG Baisheng

Chief Engineer

Mr Wang previously worked as a senior engineer at a state-owned enterprise. He joined Kemao China in 2010 and is now the Chief Engineer responsible for technical management as well as product research and development and innovation.

Mr WU Bo

Overseas Manager

Mr Wu has over 10 years experiences in foreign trade. He is fluent in English and good at cross-border business negotiations and overseas marketing. Mr Wu joined Kemao China in 2014.

Mr LIU Qinghua

Domestic Manager

Mr Liu graduated from Jiangnan University and has been working in sales and marketing for 15 years. He has been with Kemao China since 2009.
